Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:10.73,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:14.52,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}But you're fading away
