Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:55.57,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:59.04,open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You know what our lives would be
